title: "THAMIZH MCP -- a grounded Tamil word-grammar analysis server"
abstract: >-
  A Model Context Protocol server for Tamil word-grammar (chol ilakkanam)
  analysis that grounds answers in authentic Tamil sources (Tholkappiyam-first)
  and self-enriches from evolving Tamil data.
